Invoicefu,is,an,online,invoicing,service,The,service,is,best,suited,for,users,who,need,simple,invoices,It,is,web,based,and,can,be,accessed,via,any,computer,or,device,with,an,internet,connection,The,API,lets,users,access,accounts,clients,and,invoices,and,perform,standard,CRUD,operations,on,them,Developers,can,use,the,API,to,integrate,Invoicefu,with,thier,own,applications,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON